---
import Breadcrumbs from '../../components/Breadcrumbs.astro'
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro'
import AuthorBox from '../../components/AuthorBox.astro'
import FAQ from '../../components/FAQ.astro'
---
<Layout title="AI Search Visibility Pricing | Rank4AI" description="AI search visibility pricing. Ecosystem from £800/mo, full agency from £1,500/mo, advisory from £1,000/mo. Starts with a free audit.">

<section class="pt-12 pb-24 reveal">
  <div class="container-narrow">
    <Breadcrumbs items={[
      { label: 'Home', href: '/' },
      { label: 'What We Do', href: '/what-we-do/' },
      { label: 'Pricing' }
    ]} />

    <p class="section-tag">Pricing</p>
    <h1 class="mb-6">Pricing</h1>

    <div class="bg-off-white border-l-3 border-l-teal rounded-lg p-6 mb-8 mt-6">
      <p class="text-[15px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed">Ecosystem from £800/mo. Full agency from £1,500/mo. Advisory from £1,000/mo. Every engagement starts with a free audit.</p>
    </div>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-10">Every engagement starts with an AI Visibility Audit. From there, three paths: ecosystem (no site work), full agency (includes site work), or advisory (we advise, you implement).</p>
  </div>

  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="mb-8">Ecosystem Services – No Site Work</h2>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-16">
      <div class="card">
        <h3 class="!text-lg text-teal mb-1">Google Foundation</h3>
        <p class="font-display text-3xl text-teal mb-4">£800<span class="text-sm text-text-muted font-body"> / month</span></p>
        <ul class="text-sm text-text-muted space-y-2 mb-6">
          <li>AI Visibility Audit</li>
          <li>Core presence across Google platforms</li>
          <li>External directory alignment</li>
          <li>Site asset pack</li>
          <li>Monthly action document</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/free-audit/" class="link text-sm">Get started &rarr;</a>
      </div>
      <div class="card border-l-3 border-l-teal">
        <h3 class="!text-lg text-teal mb-1">Core Ecosystem</h3>
        <p class="font-display text-3xl text-teal mb-4">£1,300<span class="text-sm text-text-muted font-body"> / month</span></p>
        <ul class="text-sm text-text-muted space-y-2 mb-6">
          <li>Everything in Google Foundation</li>
          <li>Microsoft and Bing ecosystem</li>
          <li>Wider web: directories, reviews, citations</li>
          <li>All six AI platforms covered</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/free-audit/" class="link text-sm">Get started &rarr;</a>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3 class="!text-lg text-teal mb-1">Full Ecosystem</h3>
        <p class="font-display text-3xl text-teal mb-4">£2,500<span class="text-sm text-text-muted font-body"> / month</span></p>
        <ul class="text-sm text-text-muted space-y-2 mb-6">
          <li>Everything in Core Ecosystem</li>
          <li>Share of Voice PR strategy</li>
          <li>Data authority assets</li>
          <li>120-200+ active touchpoints</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/free-audit/" class="link text-sm">Get started &rarr;</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="mb-8">Full Agency – Includes Site Work</h2>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6 mb-16">
      <div class="card">
        <h3 class="!text-lg text-teal mb-1">Entry</h3>
        <p class="font-display text-2xl text-teal mb-3">From £800<span class="text-xs text-text-muted font-body"> / mo</span></p>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed">Ecosystem only. No site work. The right starting point for most businesses.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3 class="!text-lg text-teal mb-1">Standard</h3>
        <p class="font-display text-2xl text-teal mb-3">£1,500–2,500<span class="text-xs text-text-muted font-body"> / mo</span></p>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed">Audit-driven scope. Priority areas identified and addressed.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3 class="!text-lg text-teal mb-1">Strategic</h3>
        <p class="font-display text-2xl text-teal mb-3">£3,000–5,000<span class="text-xs text-text-muted font-body"> / mo</span></p>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed">Multiple areas. 80-120 touchpoints. Monthly AI testing.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3 class="!text-lg text-teal mb-1">Partner</h3>
        <p class="font-display text-2xl text-teal mb-3">£5,000+<span class="text-xs text-text-muted font-body"> / mo</span></p>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed">Complete and continuous. 120-200+ touchpoints. Weekly AI testing.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="mb-8">Advisory & Consultancy</h2>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-16">
      <div class="card">
        <h3 class="!text-lg text-teal mb-1">Essentials</h3>
        <p class="font-display text-2xl text-teal mb-3">£1,000<span class="text-xs text-text-muted font-body"> / mo</span></p>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed">Monthly strategy session. AI visibility monitoring. Quarterly briefs.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card border-l-3 border-l-teal">
        <h3 class="!text-lg text-teal mb-1">Standard</h3>
        <p class="font-display text-2xl text-teal mb-3">£2,000<span class="text-xs text-text-muted font-body"> / mo</span></p>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed">Fortnightly sessions. Full implementation briefs. Priority support.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3 class="!text-lg text-teal mb-1">Strategic</h3>
        <p class="font-display text-2xl text-teal mb-3">£3,000<span class="text-xs text-text-muted font-body"> / mo</span></p>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed">Weekly sessions. Full strategy ownership. Team training. Board reporting.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container-narrow">
      <h2 class="mb-4">Add-Ons</h2>
      <div class="card-teal-border">
        <h3 class="!text-base text-teal mb-2">Microsoft and Bing</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted">Available as a standalone add-on to any Google tier. Expands coverage into ChatGPT and Copilot directly.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>


    <!-- Internal links -->
    <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-border">
      <h2 class="!text-xl mb-4">Related</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-3">
                <a href="/what-we-do/" class="card group text-sm"><span class="font-medium text-teal group-hover:text-accent">All Services</span></a>
        <a href="/what-we-do/ai-visibility-audit/" class="card group text-sm"><span class="font-medium text-teal group-hover:text-accent">AI Visibility Audit</span></a>
        <a href="/about/five-signal-framework/" class="card group text-sm"><span class="font-medium text-teal group-hover:text-accent">The Five Signal Model</span></a>
        <a href="/free-audit/" class="card group text-sm"><span class="font-medium text-accent">Get a Free Audit &rarr;</span></a>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="bg-off-white border-t border-border text-center py-24 px-10 mt-16">
    <h2 class="mb-4">Get Started</h2>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted mb-10 max-w-[500px] mx-auto">Every engagement begins with the AI Search Visibility Audit. The audit tells us what makes sense – you choose the pace.</p>
    <a href="/free-audit/" class="cta-primary">Get a Free AI Search Visibility Audit &rarr;</a>
  </div>
  <div class="container-narrow mt-8">
    <AuthorBox />
  </div>

    <section class="mt-16 pt-12 border-t border-gray-200">
      <h2 class="mb-6">Frequently asked questions</h2>
      <FAQ items={[{"question": "How much does AI search visibility work cost?", "answer": "Full Agency starts at \u00a31,500 per month. Ecosystem Services starts at \u00a31,000 per month. Advisory starts at \u00a31,000 per month. The AI Visibility Audit is \u00a31,500 one-off. Most engagements are 6 months minimum to see compounding results."}, {"question": "Why does pricing start at \u00a31,000 per month?", "answer": "At that level we can meaningfully move 2 or 3 Five Signal scores per month. Below it, the work becomes surface-level and the results don't stick. 89% of our clients at the \u00a31,000+ tier see measurable AI citation lift within 90 days."}, {"question": "Do you offer one-off projects or only retainers?", "answer": "The AI Visibility Audit (\u00a31,500) is one-off. Everything else is monthly retainer with a 3-month minimum, ideally 6. AI search moves slowly; compounding signals need time. If you need one-off strategy, book Advisory instead."}]} />
    </section>
</section>

</Layout>
